snippet.title: Amber Heard At 2020 Spirit Awards Amid Depp's Video Release
snippet.description:
Amber Heard was spotted greeting fans at 2020 Spirit Awards with total poise amidst the Johnny Depp releasing 87 videos.  She stopped and signed for adoring fans.  The 33-year-old Aquaman actress sported a Fendi suit covered in butterflies as she stepped out for the awards event.

Who. Amber Heard

What. Greeting fans

Wearing. Fendi suit

Where? Parking Lot, Santa Monica State Beach, Santa Monica, CA 90401

#amberheard #aquaman #fendi #spiritwards2020
